title Substrate peak MgO (002) spin--
broadcast Substrate peak MgO (002) spin--
he3 polariser/spin -1
wait 2
he3 analyser/spin -1
wait 2
broadcast MgO (002) --
drive s2 -67.66
runscan s1 -10.6 -12.6 21 time 1

title Substrate peak MgO (002) spin-+
broadcast Substrate peak MgO (002) spin-+
he3 polariser/spin -1
wait 2
he3 analyser/spin 1
wait 2
broadcast MgO (002) -+
drive s2 -67.66
runscan s1 -10.6 -12.6 21 time 1

